organizing the autopsy results.

525
00:38:24,337 --> 00:38:26,105
Take care of it before sunrise tomorrow.

526
00:38:26,873 --> 00:38:29,041
The article about that bitch
needs to be in the morning paper.

527
00:38:30,409 --> 00:38:31,944
Only then is your job done.

528
00:38:32,478 --> 00:38:33,312
Yes.

529
00:38:33,312 --> 00:38:35,781
