call me, no matter how late.

531
00:38:39,619 --> 00:38:41,587
Don't you dare think of making excuses.

532
00:38:41,587 --> 00:38:42,421
Yes.

533
00:38:43,789 --> 00:38:44,757
Damn it!

534
00:39:11,584 --> 00:39:12,418
Representative Gu.

535
00:39:13,019 --> 00:39:15,188
