537
00:39:18,591 --> 00:39:20,226
Yes, I'll contact you again.

538
00:39:30,803 --> 00:39:33,339
Assemblyman Baek might get us fired,

539
00:39:34,207 --> 00:39:35,608
but Representative Gu

540
00:39:36,542 --> 00:39:37,910
will really kill us.

541
00:39:52,492 --> 00:39:54,327
Do you think this makes sense?

542
00:39:54,327 --> 00:39:56,662
