578
00:41:09,068 --> 00:41:10,169
Mr. Choi Dae-hyun.

579
00:41:10,169 --> 00:41:13,072
I'm going to be questioned anyway,
so I'll be questioned.

580
00:41:14,440 --> 00:41:17,710
Depending on your statement,
