useless card to the police.

615
00:44:04,811 --> 00:44:07,113
Do you know how
disadvantageous this is for you?

616
00:44:08,014 --> 00:44:10,416
Can't I just say I did it?

617
00:44:10,416 --> 00:44:14,086
