the request of your deceased daughter?

630
00:45:23,356 --> 00:45:25,258
Your daughter's suicide
note was found at your home.

631
00:45:25,258 --> 00:45:26,792
Why didn't you submit it earlier?

632
00:45:26,792 --> 00:45:28,461
