708
00:51:45,457 --> 00:51:46,358
Yes.

709
00:51:46,358 --> 00:51:47,660
Then if it wasn't Ms. Woo So-jeong,

710
00:51:48,394 --> 00:51:49,828
are you saying you did it, Father? Yang

711
00:51:55,367 --> 00:51:56,769
Persuade Ms. Woo So-jeong

712
00:51:58,337 --> 00:51:59,738
and help her confess.

713
00:52:00,873 --> 00:52:03,142
As things stand, reducing
her sentence is the best option.

714
00:52:03,809 --> 00:52:06,378
Dr. Woo did not kill Ms. Lee Eun-hee.

715
00:52:06,378 --> 00:52:08,013
So what are you asking
me to persuade her to do?

716
00:52:08,781 --> 00:52:11,417
Oh my, it's late.

717
00:52:11,417 --> 00:52:13,786
Let him go. He has to go, man.
 He has to pray.

718
00:52:13,786 --> 00:52:14,954
What were you doing so late?

719
00:52:14,954 --> 00:52:16,155
You can go.

720
00:52:17,823 --> 00:52:19,558
What happens to Dr. Woo?

721
00:52:19,925 --> 00:52:21,927
The questioning is over,
so you can go now.

722
00:52:21,927 --> 00:52:22,995
No, I mean...

723
00:52:23,629 --> 00:52:24,763
What about Dr. Woo?

724
00:52:26,632 --> 00:52:29,902
If Dr. Woo can't leave, then I'll stay here too.

725
00:52:31,170 --> 00:52:32,004
Father Yang.

726
00:52:32,404 --> 00:52:36,075
Do you think Woo So-jeong is under
suspicion only because of Ms. Lee Eun-hee?

727
00:52:38,711 --> 00:52:40,245
What do you mean?

728
00:52:44,850 --> 00:52:47,253
Is she involved in other cases too?

729
00:52:47,820 --> 00:52:49,989
The autopsy results will be out soon,

730
00:52:49,989 --> 00:52:51,557
so stop it and go.

731
00:52:52,024 --> 00:52:54,727
