733
00:53:03,836 --> 00:53:04,870
You should go.

734
00:53:06,572 --> 00:53:07,706
What if I did it?

735
00:53:14,513 --> 00:53:15,347
Yes.

736
00:53:17,583 --> 00:53:19,184
I killed Ms. Lee Eun-hee.

737
00:53:20,953 --> 00:53:21,954
I killed her.

738
00:53:30,562 --> 00:53:31,997
Stop it.

739
00:53:32,598 --> 00:53:34,466
