you can't help Ms. Woo So-jeong.

740
00:53:34,466 --> 00:53:35,634
No, right now,

741
00:53:36,368 --> 00:53:38,837
I'm confessing to my lawyer.

742
00:53:40,039 --> 00:53:42,741
Not just this time,
but I did all the previous cases.

743
00:53:44,109 --> 00:53:45,044
