748
00:53:59,525 --> 00:54:00,659
Euthanasia.

749
00:54:03,228 --> 00:54:04,430
I started it.

750
00:54:05,923 --> 00:54:07,499
My ex-girlfriend.

751
00:54:08,701 --> 00:54:09,535
Mi-na.

752
00:54:11,070 --> 00:54:12,271
I killed her.

753
00:54:59,118 --> 00:55:01,754
Ugh, the smell.

754
00:55:04,757 --> 00:55:06,525
A living corpse is still a living person,

755
00:55:06,525 --> 00:55:09,795
