756
00:55:19,238 --> 00:55:20,105
A gift.

757
00:55:31,884 --> 00:55:32,718
With a syringe?

758
00:55:44,229 --> 00:55:45,864
Most of them drink it with alcohol.

759
00:55:47,566 --> 00:55:49,602
Injecting it intravenously is the surest way,

760
00:55:50,235 --> 00:55:53,305
but that leaves a mark on the body.

761
00:55:54,173 --> 00:55:57,910
Benponarbital is mixed with the various
